
### .gitignore

```gitignore
# Node.js
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log

# Environment variables
.env
.env.production

# Logs
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store

# Certificates
certs/
*.cert
*.key

# Images and voice files
# Ignore all by default
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.mp3
*.wav
*.ogg

# But keep icons and manifest for the PWA in the public folder
!frontend/public/*.png
!frontend/public/*.ico
!frontend/public/manifest.json
!frontend/public/index.html

# Data (development)
backend/src/data/

# build files
build/*

